scp_grabup

Grab screenshots of a window or selection and upload via scp to a webserver.
Relies on passwordless ssh key authentication for use outside of a terminal.

Dependencies: scrot, xsel

Usage:
- Set your configuration variables - browser path, scp host/path, url base.
- Run grabup.
- Click on a window to select it, or drag to select a rectangular area.
- A browser will open to display your screenshot, and the URL is copied to the
  clipboard.
